components.text: [b][color=#000000][size=21] Manual changes: How often do manual change activities occur in the procurement process?[/size][/color][/b]

[size=15][b][color=#000000]  Change activities slow down the process significantly and introduce a doubling in cost per change activity. 
  Identifying and reducing those manual change activities reduces associated FTE cost.[/color][/b][/size]

formulas.name: Savings per Year
formulas.text: KPI("Impact: Manual changes")

components.text: [color=#000000][size=15][b]  Financial impact = Manual change activities (#) * invested effort per manual change (min) * FTE costs (<%=Currency%>/min) * realization potential (%) * time factor (x)[/b][/size][/color]

formulas.text: '<%= Currency %>'

formulas.text:
